  "sn55.29:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55",
  "sn55.29:2.1": "3. Saraṇānivagga",
  "sn55.29:3.1": "<span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"bhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | bhayaṃ or bhikkhu (pts1)\\\" id=\\\"note456\\\">29. Dutiyabhayaverūpasantasutta</span>",
  "sn55.29:4.1": "<span class=\\\"cross\\\" title=\\\"^an9.28#1 [28. Dutiyaverasutta]\\\" id=\\\"note457\\\">*</span> Sāvatthinidānaṃ … pe …",
  "sn55.29:4.2": "“yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti, imehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, ayañcassa ariyo ñāyo paññāya sudiṭṭho hoti suppaṭividdho;",
  "sn55.29:4.3": "so ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:",
  "sn55.29:4.4": "‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto;",
  "sn55.29:4.5": "sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti.",
  "sn55.29:5.1": "Navamaṃ."
}